{"tid":2014504,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[原罪] 神似習近平「形象違規」？ 中國聲樂家抖音帳號慘遭封鎖","createTime":"2020-05-13T05:33:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-13T06:16:55.000Z","uid":29917,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"2f862393753ff704a675a7978aedfadd7812c750","tid":2014504,"uid":29917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T05:33:42.000Z","msg":"長相錯了就不能用抖音嗎？中國一位旅歐聲樂家常在抖音上分享聲樂技巧，不過他的臉跟習近平簡直像到會讓人誤以為是雙胞胎兄弟，每次一被網友提到，帳號就會被封鎖，去年9月申請帳號到現在已經是第3次了。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://imgbon.com/?img=EJNY\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimgbon.com%2F%3Fimg%3DEJNY&h=fd24d0b5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n自拍影片引吭高歌，一名來自中國的旅歐聲樂家劉克清常在抖音上和網友分享短片，但從去年9月開設帳號之後好幾次遭到封鎖，原因就出在這張臉。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/05/13/2551424-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F05%2F13%2F2551424-XXL.jpg&h=f91d0ac3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n中國聲樂家劉克清：「我們美聲是不可以有這種抖音、這種顫音的。」<br />\n<br />\n早在去年開始劉克清就反應過，自己被網友說長得像中國國家主席習近平之後帳號就被封鎖，這個月他再次PO文，無奈表示已經三度被封，幾天後網友表示他的帳號已經恢復，但就怕再有人提到那不能說的3個字。<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/05/13/2551422-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F05%2F13%2F2551422-XXL.jpg&h=1620af23&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n記者：「習近平仔細察看雕塑、壁畫。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/05/13/2551423-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F05%2F13%2F2551423-XXL.jpg&h=8d85e34c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n至於習近平本人則是展開華北省份的第2次調研視察，11日到山西大同雲岡石窟，而這已經是習近平近3個月來第6次基層考察。<br />\n<br />\n由於高頻率離京考察相當罕見，習近平以往遇到統治危機時，疑似就會有藉出行避風頭的舉動，也讓外界猜測可能是因為武漢肺炎疫情，習近平面對內憂外患用來轉移目標的手段之一。（殷悅哲整理）"},{"pid":"e160a18f60a24505ae5b717cb327ad96fdedfca3","tid":2014504,"uid":197256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T05:35:01.000Z","msg":"[有片] 有手足整合左510黑警行刑式對待記者既片加埋字幕宣揚國際<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=okoY6s37JlQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DokoY6s37JlQ&d=RJ6DAKdT%2BAkj0rfdhPz9Nd%2BR0LtvndqJ8lr%2BzYsHiyM%3D&h=7e8446c6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=okoY6s37JlQ</a><br />\n幫手推上reddit, Twitter, FB<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/blackheaddown/status/1260438058631135233\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fblackheaddown%2Fstatus%2F1260438058631135233&d=RJ6DAKdT%2BAkj0rfdhPz9Nd%2BR0LtvndqJ8lr%2BzYsHiyM%3D&h=bca6d3d2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fblackheaddown%2Fstatus%2F1260438058631135233&h=653a3449\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/blackheaddown/status/1260438058631135233</a><br />\n幫幫手置頂唔該"},{"pid":"444d714e0756303fa5aba609c80960368b911a27","tid":2014504,"uid":268957,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T05:35:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.osim.com.hk/media/bannerslider/o/n/online_fa_webshop_banner_desktop_tc_7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.osim.com.hk%2Fmedia%2Fbannerslider%2Fo%2Fn%2Fonline_fa_webshop_banner_desktop_tc_7.jpg&h=2dffe625&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ef1808dd053e4bc699f67f19611edbba8da0966c","tid":2014504,"uid":42804,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T05:35:22.000Z","msg":"真係慘，生得樣衰都係罪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6fc480e13a35f82a420468245ac29bd346255c1","tid":2014504,"uid":268957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T05:36:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://scontent-hkt1-1.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/p960x960/95592766_2971628246209057_2421319445554135040_o.jpg?_nc_cat=108&amp;_nc_sid=8024bb&amp;_nc_ohc=9DfdzxwMhDEA